php-dragonmantank-cron-expression for Debian

This package installs the Cron\ namespace under /usr/share/php/Cron and
registers its autoloader through pkg-php-tools.

For direct use without Composer, include:
    require_once '/usr/share/php/Cron/autoload.php';

